rComments: She's a good prof. She teaches advanced grammar in Spanish well and gives clear powerpoints. She gives many practice exercises to help you prepare for tests. She's always willing to assist students when needed. Beware of this: she gives out A LOT of assignments and tests which makes you work for it. She's a fair marker as well.
teacherRatingTags: ['Test heavy', 'Accessible outside class', 'Get ready to read']
